info.description:
- Collection:
    

OrderCreation_WF

- Systems:
    

Acuity + AWS S3 bucket

- Description:
    

This collection allow us to create orders in Acuity and upload JSON template file into AWS S3 bucket. This Test Data helps us to verify the Desktop's SmartTag functionality.
